trigger.name: trigger

revisions.description: MIB revision history dates in descriptions updated.
Added trigger configuration details for AW+

trigger.description: This MIB file contains definitions of managed objects for the TRIGGER module.

triggerTrap.name: triggerTrap
triggerTrap.description: A trigger trap is generated a trigger is activated. The number of the trigger activated is given by the variable triggerLastTriggerActivated.

triggerLastTriggerActivated.name: triggerLastTriggerActivated
triggerLastTriggerActivated.description: The trigger number of the most recent trigger activated on this router. This is also the variable sent in the trigger trap below. If no triggers have been activated yet since the last restart of this router, this variable will read as 0.

triggerConfigInfoTable.name: triggerConfigInfoTable
triggerConfigInfoTable.description: The (conceptual) table listing entries of trigger configuration details.

triggerConfigInfoEntry.name: triggerConfigInfoEntry
triggerConfigInfoEntry.description: An entry (conceptual row) in the triggerConfigInfoTable.

triggerNumber.name: triggerNumber
triggerNumber.description: The object represents the ID number of the trigger.

triggerName.name: triggerName
triggerName.description: This object represents the name and description of the trigger.

triggerTypeDetail.name: triggerTypeDetail
triggerTypeDetail.description: This object indicates the trigger type and its activation conditions.

triggerActiveDaysOrDate.name: triggerActiveDaysOrDate
triggerActiveDaysOrDate.description: This objects indicates either the days of a week or the date, on which the trigger is permitted to activate.

triggerActivateAfter.name: triggerActivateAfter
triggerActivateAfter.description: This object indicates the time when the trigger will be activated afterwards.

triggerActivateBefore.name: triggerActivateBefore
triggerActivateBefore.description: This object indicates the time when the trigger will be activated before.

triggerActiveStatus.name: triggerActiveStatus
triggerActiveStatus.description: This object indicates whether or not the trigger is permitted to activate.

triggerTestMode.name: triggerTestMode
triggerTestMode.description: This object indicates whether or not the trigger is operating in diagnostic mode.

triggerSnmpTrap.name: triggerSnmpTrap
triggerSnmpTrap.description: This object indicates whether or not a snmp trap will be sent when the trigger is activated.

triggerRepeatTimes.name: triggerRepeatTimes
triggerRepeatTimes.description: This objects indicates whether the trigger repeats an unlimited number of times (continuous) or for a set of times. When the trigger can repeat only a set of times, then the number of times the trigger has been activated is displayed in brackets.

triggerLasttimeModified.name: triggerLasttimeModified
triggerLasttimeModified.description: This object indicates the date and time of the last time that the trigger was modified.

triggerNumberOfActivation.name: triggerNumberOfActivation
triggerNumberOfActivation.description: The objects represents the number of times the trigger has been activated since the last restart of the device.

triggerLasttimeActivation.name: triggerLasttimeActivation
triggerLasttimeActivation.description: This object indicates the date and time of the last time that the trigger was activated.

triggerNumberOfScripts.name: triggerNumberOfScripts
triggerNumberOfScripts.description: This objects represents the number of scripts that are associated with this trigger.

triggerScript1.name: triggerScript1
triggerScript1.description: This objects represents the name of the 1st script that is associated with the trigger.

triggerScript2.name: triggerScript2
triggerScript2.description: This objects represents the name of the 2nd script that is associated with the trigger.

triggerScript3.name: triggerScript3
triggerScript3.description: This objects represents the name of the 3rd script that is associated with the trigger.

triggerScript4.name: triggerScript4
triggerScript4.description: This objects represents the name of the 4th script that is associated with the trigger.

triggerScript5.name: triggerScript5
triggerScript5.description: This objects represents the name of the 5th script that is associated with the trigger.

triggerNumOfActivation.name: triggerNumOfActivation
triggerNumOfActivation.description: This objects represents the number of times a trigger has been activated.

triggerNumOfActivationToday.name: triggerNumOfActivationToday
triggerNumOfActivationToday.description: This objects represents the number of times a trigger has been activated today.

triggerNumOfPerodicActivationToday.name: triggerNumOfPerodicActivationToday
triggerNumOfPerodicActivationToday.description: This objects represents the number of times a periodic trigger has been activated today.

triggerNumOfInterfaceActivationToday.name: triggerNumOfInterfaceActivationToday
triggerNumOfInterfaceActivationToday.description: This objects represents the number of times an interface trigger has been activated today.

triggerNumOfResourceActivationToday.name: triggerNumOfResourceActivationToday
triggerNumOfResourceActivationToday.description: This objects represents the number of times a CPU or memory trigger has been activated today.

triggerNumOfRebootActivationToday.name: triggerNumOfRebootActivationToday
triggerNumOfRebootActivationToday.description: This objects represents the number of times a reboot trigger has been activated today.

triggerNumOfPingPollActivationToday.name: triggerNumOfPingPollActivationToday
triggerNumOfPingPollActivationToday.description: This objects represents the number of times a ping-poll trigger has been activated today.

triggerNumOfStackMasterFailActivationTod.name: triggerNumOfStackMasterFailActivationToday
triggerNumOfStackMasterFailActivationTod.description: This objects represents the number of times a stack master fail trigger has been activated today.

triggerNumOfStackMemberActivationToday.name: triggerNumOfStackMemberActivationToday
triggerNumOfStackMemberActivationToday.description: This objects represents the number of times a stack member trigger has been activated today.

triggerNumOfStackXemStkActivationToday.name: triggerNumOfStackXemStkActivationToday
triggerNumOfStackXemStkActivationToday.description: This objects represents the number of times a stack xem-stack trigger has been activated today.
